<plot>In the world of avatars, you are who you pretend to be. But who are you when you stop pretending? Lisa is about to find out. She's caught Tyler, her husband, cheating on her in cyberspace, and now Lisa is turning the tables on TyMeUp. In one electric week, Lisa, falls head over heels for one avatar while being stalked by another. When they meet on a blind date, Lisa discovers that two online wrongs CAN make a right. For avatars, any resemblance to fictional characters is purely intentional.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?052396</url></doc>
